---
description: Apply unit testing standards to isolate and verify individual code units. Focus on mocking dependencies, testing edge cases, and maintaining fast, independent tests.
globs: apps/**/*.unit.*
alwaysApply: false
---

Isolation and Focus:
- Test one functional unit only.
- Mock all external dependencies.
- Keep tests fast and independent.

Coverage:
- Test edge cases thoroughly.
- Verify error handling conditions.

Robustness:
- Avoid brittle assertion checks (e.g., exact messages).
